OL,3,CSouthampton knock Premier League
OL,4,Cleaders Arsenal out of FA Cup
OL,6,FSouthampton has stunned Premier League
OL,7,Fleaders Arsenal, knocking them out of
OL,8,Fthe FA Cup and dashing the Gunners'
OL,9,Fdreams of a treble.
OL,11,FFans at St Mary's Stadium erupted as
OL,12,Fsuper sub Shea Charles fired the late
OL,13,Fwinner, and firing the Saints to
OL,14,FWembley.
OL,16,FThe Championship side are the only non-
OL,17,FPremier League side left in the
OL,18,Fcompetition, following Port Vale's 7-0
OL,19,Fdefeat to Chelsea earlier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
