OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775426988
OL,3,CSouthampton knock Premier League
OL,4,Cleaders Arsenal out of FA Cup
OL,6,FIt is the third time they have reached
OL,7,Fthe cup semi-finals in the last 10
OL,8,Fyears - another chance to see if they
OL,9,Fcan replicate their famous FA Cup win
OL,10,Fin 1976.
OL,12,FMikel Arteta's Gunners arrived at St
OL,13,FMary's as overwhelming favourites,
OL,14,Fstill hanging on to hopes of a treble
OL,15,Fafter their Carabao Cup final defeat
OL,16,Fto Manchester City a fortnight ago.
OL,18,FRoss Stewart put Southampton ahead in
OL,19,Fthe first half, sparking bedlam around
OL,20,Fthe stadium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
