FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775426988
OL,3,CSouthampton knock Premier League
OL,4,Cleaders Arsenal out of FA Cup
OL,6,FArsenal failed to really threaten,
OL,7,Funtil Arteta made a triple change.
OL,8,FGyokeres levelled the score minutes
OL,9,Fafter he was subbed on.
OL,11,FThe Gunners had some near goals, but
OL,12,Fit was Shea Charles who came off the
OL,13,Fbench to land the knockout blow.
OL,15,FIt was just a fifth defeat of the
OL,16,Fcampaign for Arsenal, who sit nine
OL,17,Fpoints clear at the top of the Premier
OL,18,FLeague but have plenty of soul
OL,19,Fsearching to do after costly back-to-
OL,20,Fback cup losses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
